-- Statement: WHILE
-- Grammar rule: whileStatement (TSql170.g)
-- Doc: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/t-sql/language-elements/while-transact-sql

-- From TSql170.g:
whileStatement:
    While booleanExpression
    statementOptSemi
    ;

-- Sub-rules referenced:
-- booleanExpression: (defined elsewhere - complex boolean expression grammar)
-- statementOptSemi: a single T-SQL statement with optional semicolon

-- From Microsoft docs:
-- WHILE boolean_expression
--     { sql_statement | statement_block | BREAK | CONTINUE }
